ks. \u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eThe author has an easy voice to read, and tells the stories clearly and honestly. She won the Nobel Peace Prize in 2011. What a story of powerful women leading the way.","rating":4,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/388066?shelf=read"},"taggings":[],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/4255761317"},"likeCount":2,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":0,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.-KtxLqENWG8RtpBXJvMZpg":{"id":"kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.-KtxLqENWG8RtpBXJvMZpg","__typename":"Book"},"User:16237436":{"id":16237436,"__typename":"User","legacyId":16237436,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1471720785i/16237436._UX200_CR0,0,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":false,"textReviewsCount":922,"viewableName":"Birgitte Bach","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/16237436-birgitte-bach","contributor":null,"isFollowing":false,"isFriend":false,"followersCount":20},"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.dgmGpjCkG3RVBVk4H1Te2Q":{"id":"kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.dgmGpjCkG3RVBVk4H1Te2Q","__typename":"Review","book":{"__ref":"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.-KtxLqENWG8RtpBXJvMZpg"},"creator":{"__ref":"User:16237436"},"recommendFor":null,"updatedAt":1519242570327,"createdAt":1519129037075,"spoilerStatus":false,"lastRevisionAt":1519129183831,"text":"Beundringsværdig og modig kvinde, der skriver åbent og ærligt om sine fejl og personlige nedture, som hun får vendt til et helt fantastisk og inspirerende arbejde for bedre rettigheder for kvinder og for fred i de borgerkrigs hærgede lande i Afrika.","rating":5,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/16237436?shelf=read"},"taggings":[],"we